---
/**
 * NoteLifecycle — visual map of how a vault note evolves over time.
 * Four operations (correct, invalidate, supersede, forget) shown as
 * transitions out of an "active" state.
 */
---

<figure class="lifecycle" role="img" aria-label="Note lifecycle: active state and four transitions (correct, invalidate, supersede, forget)">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 760 420" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <defs>
      <radialGradient id="lf-active" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="var(--sl-color-accent)" stop-opacity="0.28"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="var(--sl-color-accent)" stop-opacity="0.04"/>
      </radialGradient>
      <marker id="lf-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5"
              markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto">
        <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="var(--sl-color-accent)"/>
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <!-- Active state (center) -->
    <g class="lf-state">
      <circle cx="380" cy="200" r="80" fill="url(#lf-active)"
              stroke="var(--sl-color-accent)" stroke-width="1.4"/>
      <text x="380" y="195" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Fraunces Variable, Georgia, serif"
            font-size="18" font-weight="500" fill="var(--sl-color-text)"
            font-style="italic">active</text>
      <text x="380" y="216" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="11"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55">status: stable</text>
    </g>

    <!-- Four endpoint states -->
    <g class="lf-state">
      <!-- corrected (same note, edited) -->
      <rect x="40" y="40" width="180" height="74" rx="6"
            fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.025)" stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.25"/>
      <text x="130" y="65" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="JetBrains Mono Variable, monospace"
            font-size="11" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.14em"
            fill="var(--sl-color-accent)">CORRECT</text>
      <text x="130" y="84" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10.5"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.75">edit in place</text>
      <text x="130" y="100" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55">corrections[] grows</text>

      <!-- invalidated (kept, marked dead) -->
      <rect x="540" y="40" width="180" height="74" rx="6"
            fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.025)" stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.25"/>
      <text x="630" y="65" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="JetBrains Mono Variable, monospace"
            font-size="11" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.14em"
            fill="var(--sl-color-accent)">INVALIDATE</text>
      <text x="630" y="84" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10.5"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.75">status: invalid</text>
      <text x="630" y="100" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55">history visible</text>

      <!-- superseded (decisions only, bidirectional link) -->
      <rect x="40" y="290" width="180" height="74" rx="6"
            fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.025)" stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.25"/>
      <text x="130" y="315" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="JetBrains Mono Variable, monospace"
            font-size="11" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.14em"
            fill="var(--sl-color-accent)">SUPERSEDE</text>
      <text x="130" y="334" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10.5"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.75">old ↔ new ADR</text>
      <text x="130" y="350" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55">decisions only</text>

      <!-- forgotten (moved to trash) -->
      <rect x="540" y="290" width="180" height="74" rx="6"
            fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.025)" stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.25"/>
      <text x="630" y="315" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="JetBrains Mono Variable, monospace"
            font-size="11" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.14em"
            fill="var(--sl-color-accent)">FORGET</text>
      <text x="630" y="334" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10.5"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.75">→ .trash/</text>
      <text x="630" y="350" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55">PHI · secrets · mistakes</text>
    </g>

    <!-- Transition arrows from active out to each -->
    <g stroke="var(--sl-color-accent)" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none"
       opacity="0.7" marker-end="url(#lf-arrow)">
      <path d="M 320 165 Q 240 130 220 105"/>
      <path d="M 440 165 Q 520 130 540 105"/>
      <path d="M 320 235 Q 240 280 220 305"/>
      <path d="M 440 235 Q 520 280 540 305"/>
    </g>

    <!-- Transition labels -->
    <g font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10.5"
       fill="currentColor" font-style="italic" opacity="0.7"
       paint-order="stroke" stroke="var(--sl-color-bg)" stroke-width="3">
      <text x="245" y="155" text-anchor="middle">one paragraph wrong</text>
      <text x="515" y="155" text-anchor="middle">whole note stale</text>
      <text x="245" y="263" text-anchor="middle">new ADR replaces</text>
      <text x="515" y="263" text-anchor="middle">must disappear</text>
    </g>

    <!-- Audit trail rail at bottom -->
    <g>
      <line x1="40" y1="395" x2="720" y2="395" stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-opacity="0.12"/>
      <text x="380" y="412" text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Inter Variable, sans-serif" font-size="10"
            fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55" font-style="italic">
        every transition writes to corrections[] / superseded_by / .trash log — nothing happens silently
      </text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption>
    Four ways knowledge changes. Each operation leaves a different audit
    trail, so the vault's history stays legible even as content evolves.
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .lifecycle {
    margin: 2rem auto;
    max-width: 50rem;
  }
  .lifecycle svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    color: var(--sl-color-text);
  }
  .lifecycle figcaption {
    font-family: var(--strata-font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 24;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
</style>
